These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-1::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, dressmaker
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: lacrosse, soccer
1. the dressmaker is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Job           | dressmaker | designer |
| Sport   | soccer     | lacrosse  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-2::.
2 different pets are kept: goat, lizard
There are 2 different favourite colors: fuchsia, grey
1. the person who likes fuchsia is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goat##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |
| Pet         | lizard   | goat      |
| Color   | fuchsia | grey |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: r&b, rock
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: azalea, begonia
1. the fan of r&b is somewhere to the right of the person who growsazalea##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2    |
| Music-Genre   | rock | r&b    |
| Flower     | azalea | begonia |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-4::.
