.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-5::.
There 2 different types of food: lemon, orange
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, ship
1. the person eating lemon is somewhere to the right of the person driving the ship##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |
| Food   | orange | lemon |
| Transport     | ship    | bus    |

