.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-10::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: country, disco
There are 2 different nationalities: american, argentine
1. the argentine is somewhere to the left of the american##5
2. the fan of country is somewhere to the right of the fan of disco##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | disco | country |
| Nationality     | argentine   | american    |

 #################################

 
